title: Brett Battles - Jonathan Quinn  Books 1-10  EPUB
description:
Jonathan Quinn is a peculiar professional who does a job anybody else hardly dare to take up. He is a 'Cleaner'  who cleans up   the murder locations to ensure the killers' tracks are covered. He gets his call for action at the end of each assassination  job he is hired to assist with. But unlike other cleaners, Quinn tend to entangle himself in strange happenstances that pushes him to the limits of questioning the morals  of their world.
Brett Battles is the Barry Award-winning author of eighteen novels, including the Jonathan Quinn series, the Logan Harper series, and the Project Eden series. You can learn more at his website: www.brettbattles.com
